<div class="popup" id="popup">
    <div class="popup-content">
        <h2>Just Us üíñ</h2>
        <p>
            Some feelings don‚Äôt need a reason.<br><br>
            They just exist ‚Äî quietly,<br>
            like us.
        </p>
        <button onclick="closePopup(event)">Stay</button>
    </div>
